Name: Galactic Force
About the game: Are you ready to show that you are indeed the best shooter in the galaxy? Galactic Force is here to test all your capabilities and take your attacks to the next level. If you always wanted to enjoy an extraordinary, action packed game experience in outer space, Galactic Force is here to offer that right away! If you always loved action packed space shooters, don’t hesitate to check out Galactic Force. This is a very interesting, intense and fun game you will play very often. Features: • A variety of weapons • Game modes: Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch, Battle Royale, Coop Survival • A smooth fast paced gaming experience • 3 Playable classes: Fighter, Tank, Sniper • Player abilities • Power-ups
